{"_id":"cbe485f3896fe74e","name":"Improved Levitate","type":"feat","img":"systems/foundryvtt-swse/assets/icons/force-technique.png","system":{"featType":"force","benefit":"If you are moved into a pit or off another elevated surface involuntarily, such as being the target of a Force Thrust or Bantha Rush, you can spend a Force Point to activate the Levitate Force Power as a Reaction.","prerequisite":"Levitate","special":"If you do so, you end your forced movement in the last square before the edge of the precipice.","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Clone Wars Campaign Guide","page":0,"tags":["force-technique"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"description":"<p>If you are moved into a pit or off another elevated surface involuntarily, such as being the target of a Force Thrust or Bantha Rush, you can spend a Force Point to activate the Levitate Force Power as a Reaction.</p><p><strong>Special:</strong> If you do so, you end your forced movement in the last square before the edge of the precipice.</p><p><strong>Related Power:</strong> Levitate</p><p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Levitate</p>","relatedPower":"Levitate"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
